snippet.title: Brixity NEW Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the latest trailer for Brixity, Devsisters' upcoming game where you get to build your own city, Brix by Brix! In development for iOS and Android devices!

More info on our official homepage:
https://www.playbrixity.com
Also follow us on Twitter:
https://www.twitter.com/playbrixity
